# Prompt Workflow

At the end of a substantial chat:

- Update durable learnings in the appropriate files under `docs/`.
- Update `prompts/current/project-state.md` if the repo state changed.
- Update `prompts/current/next-chat.md` with the best next prompt.
- Update `prompts/current/backlog.md` if priorities changed.
- Add a short checkpoint under `docs/checkpoints/` when a milestone is reached.

Do not rewrite archived prompt files after they are archived.
